From ee7d0323efe922a6a27f633b428fb926b6300fe8 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "Ryan X. Charles" <ryan@ryanxcharles.com>
Date: Sat, 23 May 2026 05:44:25 -0500
Subject: [PATCH 14/84] Clean popup trace scaffolds

Old watchers packed their clipboards away,
While popups kept their place in the play.
The date box still knows where to stand,
The Shell still dodges every hand.
---
